  "description": "<i>Alnam no Kiba</i> is a remake of the <a href=\"https://www.mobygames.com/game/turbografx-cd/alnam-no-kiba-jzoku-jnishinto-densetsu_\">PC Engine RPG</a> of the same title from two years prior. The same general plot is present, but the entire game has been reworked from a traditional Japanese-style RPG into a Japanese-style adventure or visual novel game. The player controls Kenbu as he explores various locales, speaking to other characters, and sometimes ending up with them tagging along with him.<br><br>Much of the original game's assets have been reused, but there are also some new graphics and music as well as some differences in the story, creating a very different alternate version of the game. As a bonus, there is also a gallery of fan art with commentary included on the disc.",
